<body>

<h1>PACE Micro‑Interventions</h1>

<h2>Grounding</h2>
<p>Notice your feet on the floor and take one slow breath.</p>
<p>Name three things you can see, two you can feel, one you can hear.</p>

<h2>Acceptance</h2>
<p>It makes sense you’d feel this way given the work you do.</p>

<h2>Curiosity</h2>
<p>If you were gently curious about this feeling, what might it be pointing to?</p>

<h2>Empathy</h2>
<p>What would you say to a colleague in your position?</p>

</body>
